name: Tukad Tista

review 1: Incredible place! The path there is very tricky, ask the locals to help you and they will guide you there and are good for motivation, they don't expect anything for guiding you. Wear sturdy footwear though as parts can be slippery especially if there's been recent rainfall.

review 3: A very complicated hike I would nearly say climb. I would highly recommend to get these ladies down there as a guide for 100k. Me and my girlfriend there doing it alone and at some point it was complicated to find the right way. But after the 30-45 minutes hike u find a unbelievable beautiful view. You should be completely alone up there!
